## üé≠ **Animation & Interaction Libraries**

### **AOS (Animate On Scroll)**
- **Library**: [AOS - Animate On Scroll](https://michalsnik.github.io/aos/)
- **Author**: Micha≈Ç Sajn√≥g
- **License**: MIT License
- **Version**: 2.3.1
- **Usage**: Traditional Thai-inspired scroll animations
```html
<link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.js"></script>
```
```javascript
AOS.init({
  duration: 1200,
  easing: 'ease-in-out-sine',
  once: true,
  offset: 120
});
```

### **Swiper.js**
- **Library**: [Swiper](https://swiperjs.com/)
- **License**: MIT License
- **Version**: 8.4.5
- **Usage**: Cultural image galleries, festival carousels
```javascript
const swiper = new Swiper('.blessing-carousel', {
  slidesPerView: 1,
  spaceBetween: 30,
  loop: true,
  autoplay: {
    delay: 3000,
    disableOnInteraction: false,
  },
  pagination: {
    el: '.swiper-pagination',
    clickable: true,
  }
});
```

### **GSAP (GreenSock Animation Platform)**
- **Library**: [GSAP](https://greensock.com/gsap/)
- **License**: Standard License (Free for non-commercial)
- **Usage**: Complex Thai cultural element animations
```javascript
gsap.from(".lotus-animation", {
  duration: 2,
  y: 50,
  opacity: 0,
  stagger: 0.2,
  ease: "power2.out"
});
```

