## üé® **Color Schemes & Thai Design Inspiration**

### **Traditional Thai Color Palette**
- **Thai Royal Colors**
  - Reference: [Thai Royal Color Symbolism](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thai_royal_and_noble_titles)
  - Usage: Gold (#FFD700), Royal Blue (#003366), Saffron (#FF9933)
  ```css
  :root {
    --thai-gold: #FFD700;
    --royal-blue: #003366;
    --saffron: #FF9933;
    --temple-red: #CC0000;
    --lotus-pink: #FFB6C1;
    --bamboo-green: #228B22;
  }
  ```

### **Buddhist Color Symbolism**
- **Reference**: [Buddhist Color Meanings](https://www.buddhanet.net/e-learning/history/b_color.htm)
- **Usage**: Spiritual section color schemes, meditation areas
  - White: Purity and enlightenment
  - Yellow/Gold: Middle path, freedom from material needs
  - Red: Life force, preservation
  - Blue: Infinite space, wisdom

