### **Intersection Observer API**
- **Web API**: [Intersection Observer](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Intersection_Observer_API)
- **Usage**: Lazy loading Thai cultural images, scroll-triggered animations
```javascript
const imageObserver = new IntersectionObserver((entries, observer) => {
  entries.forEach(entry => {
    if (entry.isIntersecting) {
      const img = entry.target;
      img.src = img.dataset.src;
      img.classList.add('fade-in');
      observer.unobserve(img);
    }
  });
}, {
  rootMargin: '50px 0px',
  threshold: 0.1
});
```

### **Web Storage API**
- **Local Storage**: [MDN Web Storage](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Storage_API)
- **Usage**: User preferences, visited blessings, language settings
```javascript
const userPreferences = {
  saveLanguage(lang) {
    localStorage.setItem('siamBlessing_language', lang);
  },
  
  getLanguage() {
    return localStorage.getItem('siamBlessing_language') || 'th';
  },
  
  saveFavoriteBlessings(blessings) {
    localStorage.setItem('siamBlessing_favorites', JSON.stringify(blessings));
  }
};
```

