## üì± **Progressive Web App Features**

### **Service Worker for Cultural Content**
- **Offline Cultural Experience**
  - Reference: [Google PWA Guide](https://developers.google.com/web/progressive-web-apps)
  - Usage: Offline access to blessings, cultural information
```javascript
// Cache Thai cultural content
const CULTURAL_CACHE = 'siam-blessing-cultural-v1';
const culturalAssets = [
  '/blessings/',
  '/festivals/',
  '/traditions/',
  '/assets/images/thai-cultural/',
  '/assets/audio/traditional-music/'
];

self.addEventListener('install', event => {
  event.waitUntil(
    caches.open(CULTURAL_CACHE)
      .then(cache => cache.addAll(culturalAssets))
  );
});
```

### **Web App Manifest**
- **Thai Cultural App Identity**
```json
{
  "name": "Siam Blessing - Thai Cultural Heritage",
  "short_name": "Siam Blessing",
  "description": "Discover Thai traditions, festivals, and blessings",
  "start_url": "/",
  "display": "standalone",
  "theme_color": "#FFD700",
  "background_color": "#003366",
  "lang": "th",
  "icons": [
    {
      "src": "/assets/icons/lotus-192.png",
      "sizes": "192x192",
      "type": "image/png",
      "purpose": "any maskable"
    }
  ]
}
